lead_paragraph: Nico Rosberg's first Formula One championship has had the side-effect of returning an unwanted accolade -- the most successful grand prix driver never to win the title -- to Britain's Stirling Moss.

headline.print_headline: Moss Regains Unwanted F1 Record After Rosberg Title
